      "rationale": "FDA GCBP experimental data were collected at flow rates of 2.5, 3.5, 4.5, 5.5, and 6.5 L/min at 2500 and 3500 RPM. CFD boundary conditions replicate these conditions; inlet/outlet pressure uncertainty is ±2 mmHg, within acceptable range."
